	<h1 class="story-header">Scottish Independence: Referendum preparation &#039;encouraging&#039;</h1>

     
         
 
    
    
		
        <div class="caption body-width">
  <img src="http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/69845000/jpg/_69845848_017556521-1.jpg" width="464" height="261" alt="Children running alongside sign showing referendum date" />

    <span style="width:464px;">Preparations for the referendum were said to be progressing well</span>
  </div>
<div class="embedded-hyper">
	<a class="hidden" href="#story_continues_1">Continue reading the main story</a>	




		     <div class="hyperpuff">
	       	          

		
		
						
		<!-- Non specific version -->
		
	
						<h2><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/16630456">Scotland&#039;s Future</a></h2>
		
		

		  	  <ul>
	  	  	
	   




	


	




<li>
	<a class="story" rel="published-1379926691926" href="/news/uk-scotland-scotland-politics-24203180">Guarantee made on post-Yes pensions</a>

